.TH STILL_CLIENT 1 "February 2026" "ws-camerad 1.0.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
still_client \- capture still images from ws-camerad
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B still_client
[\fIsocket_path\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B still_client
connects to the ws-camerad daemon and requests capture of a still JPEG image.
.PP
The captured image is saved to the daemon's configured stills directory.
.SH ARGUMENTS
.TP
.I socket_path
Path to daemon control socket (default: /run/ws-camerad/control.sock)
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
Capture a still image:
.B still_client
.TP
Using a custom socket:
.B still_client /tmp/custom.sock
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR ws-camerad (8),
.BR clip_client (1),
.BR frame_consumer (1)
.SH AUTHOR
Camera Daemon Contributors
